Title: Day 2: 12:00 P.M.-1:00 P.M.
Plot:
George refuses to allow Jack to assist in Nina's interrogation.  Jack resorts to blackmail to change George's mind.

Palmer and Stanton meet with a Middle Eastern ambassador who may be in league with Second Wave.

Tony visits the Warner home and questions Reza about his possible connection with Syed Ali.
